<br>Fall 1999, Section 3650, Tu & Th 11:15-12:30, PY 226
<p>SCHEDULE
</h2>
This schedule is subject to change.  Changes will be announced in
class and posted on the web.
</center>

<p>
The course schedule is divided into four parts:
<ul>
<li>
<a href="#partI">
Part I: Ambiguity in Perception
</a>
<li>
<a href="#partII">
Part II: Uncertainty in Memory
</a>
<li>
<a href="#partIII">
Part III: Ambiguity in Interpretation
</a>
<li>
<a href="#partIV">
Part IV: Uncertainty in Reasoning
</a>
</ul>

