<td colspan=2>
Categorization: <a href="scimeth.html">Concept learning and scientific 
method</a>; basic level categories; typicality effects. Categorization is 
an inference about, i.e. an interpretation of, ambiguous stimuli. 
</td>
<tr>
<td align=center>Th 28 Oct</td> 
<td align=center>8</td> 
<td colspan=2>
<a href="catmodels.html">Models of categorization (rules, prototypes
or exemplars).</a>
Semantic organization: Memory for organized
material;  the hierarchical effect.
</td> 
</tr>

